- Qin Luan.
- Yes.

55
00:04:03,740 --> 00:04:07,439
Didn't you say that Commandery Prince An was making up a story to frame you?

56
00:04:07,439 --> 00:04:09,509
During the years when you were in charge of the Palace Domestic Service,

57
00:04:09,509 --> 00:04:13,439
one of your subordinates killed an imperial doctor

58
00:04:13,440 --> 00:04:17,180
and attempted to frame Princess Xiping, Commandery Prince An, and his brother.

59
