[Episode 34]

66
00:06:25,750 --> 00:06:27,450
Han Ji.

67
00:06:28,910 --> 00:06:30,510
Your Majesty.

68
00:06:31,100 --> 00:06:33,540
As the Minister of Justice,

69
00:06:33,540 --> 00:06:36,240
