71
00:06:40,250 --> 00:06:41,959
Ponder over your mistakes in your room for half a month.

72
00:06:41,959 --> 00:06:44,700
Come back to see me after you think it through!

73
00:06:44,700 --> 00:06:46,620
Thank you, Your Majesty.

74
00:07:02,190 --> 00:07:03,890
Commandery Prince An.

75
00:07:05,150 --> 00:07:06,950
Sorry.

76
00:07:26,530 --> 00:07:30,249
Qin Luan's case was a long time ago and it involves many parties.

77
00:07:30,250 --> 00:07:32,759
Xiao Heng was also involved in it.

78
00:07:32,759 --> 00:07:36,250
It's improper for his son to carry out the investigation.

79
00:07:36,250 --> 00:07:40,379
Senior Jing, you are highly respected among the officials.

80
00:07:40,379 --> 00:07:43,400
I'll let you take charge of the investigation.

81
00:07:43,400 --> 00:07:45,939
The Ministry of Justice, the Censorate, the Court of Judicial Review,

82
00:07:45,940 --> 00:07:47,719
and the Three Judicial Offices shall assist in the investigation.

83
00:07:47,719 --> 00:07:50,289
You must find out what Qin Luan did

84
00:07:50,290 --> 00:07:53,960
and every person who is involved in the case!

85
00:07:54,590 --> 00:07:56,810
Yes, Your Majesty.

86
00:08:06,380 --> 00:08:09,280
Senior Jing, Qin Luan's reaction was not quite right.

87
00:08:09,280 --> 00:08:10,909
He must have prepared something.

88
00:08:10,909 --> 00:08:12,510
Be careful.

89
00:08:20,490 --> 00:08:22,390
Your Highness.

90
00:08:22,390 --> 00:08:25,360
How is the plan going?

91
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:26,850
The news from Zhou Han

92
00:08:26,850 --> 00:08:31,289
said that Qin Luan was counter-attacked by Xiao Jinyu and was arrested.

93
00:08:31,289 --> 00:08:32,859
Then act on the plan.

94
00:08:32,860 --> 00:08:34,360
Yes.

95
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:37,240
Where is Zhou Han?

96
00:08:39,880 --> 00:08:43,220
Mother, you got frightened today because of me. It's my fault.

97
00:08:43,730 --> 00:08:45,199
What are you doing?

98
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:48,180
Get up. Get up now.

99
00:08:51,990 --> 00:08:54,750
You saved me today.

100
00:08:54,750 --> 00:08:57,839
You also convinced the emperor to conduct a thorough investigation.

101
00:08:57,840 --> 00:08:59,989
I should thank you two on behalf of Prince Consort,

102
00:08:59,990 --> 00:09:02,639
the Chen clan, and the 20,000 loyal and righteous soldiers

103
00:09:02,639 --> 00:09:04,840
of the Military Commissioner of Jiannan.

104
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:13,929
Your Grace, Prince Consort wore it all the time when he was alive.

105
00:09:15,770 --> 00:09:18,149
He left it to me before he died.

106
00:09:18,150 --> 00:09:21,250
Now it's time to give it to you.

107
00:09:40,780 --> 00:09:43,099
Is this made of stone?

108
00:09:43,099 --> 00:09:44,880
Yes, stone.

109
00:09:44,880 --> 00:09:46,320
Where did you get the stone?

110
00:09:46,320 --> 00:09:48,520
I picked it up by the koi pond in my house.

111
00:09:49,170 --> 00:09:51,330
You are really frank.

112
00:09:59,880 --> 00:10:01,920
I'm glad you are back.

113
00:10:02,660 --> 00:10:06,580
You have suffered a lot along the way.

114
00:10:08,230 --> 00:10:10,000
The traitors have been removed,

115
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:13,800
the truth will come to light one day.

116
00:10:13,800 --> 00:10:18,330
Jinyu, there is one thing

117
00:10:19,180 --> 00:10:20,889
I need to tell you now.

118
00:10:20,889 --> 00:10:24,040
Mother, I know it.

119
00:10:24,040 --> 00:10:26,580
I am a descendant of the Chen family.

120
00:10:29,230 --> 00:10:31,280
How do you know it?

121
00:10:31,300 --> 00:10:33,900
When Chu Chu first saw you at the Imperial Medical Service,

122
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:37,200
she knew you and Father were not my biological parents

123
00:10:37,280 --> 00:10:39,350
from your looks.

124
00:10:40,650 --> 00:10:43,109
Your Grace, His Highness asked me to tell him.

125
00:10:43,110 --> 00:10:45,110
I couldn't lie to him.

126
00:10:46,350 --> 00:10:48,639
You went through fire and water with Jinyu

127
00:10:48,640 --> 00:10:50,600
and you always put Jinyu first.

128
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:53,090
How would I blame you?

129
00:10:53,090 --> 00:10:54,900
Mother, please rest assured.

130
00:10:54,900 --> 00:10:58,779
Before I came, Senior Jing asked me to tell you that he had asked the emperor.

131
00:10:58,779 --> 00:11:00,599
If it was a miscarriage of justice

132
00:11:00,600 --> 00:11:03,900
that you protected the descendant of a royal general. It's a good deed.

133
00:11:05,010 --> 00:11:06,329
I don't care about that.

134
00:11:06,329 --> 00:11:10,649
It's just I've been feeling guilty.

135
00:11:10,649 --> 00:11:12,370
During all these years,

136
00:11:12,370 --> 00:11:15,229
I couldn't let you fulfill your filial duties to your parents.

137
00:11:15,230 --> 00:11:19,050
We had no choice back then.

138
00:11:19,570 --> 00:11:23,329
Now that you know who your biological parents are,

139
00:11:23,329 --> 00:11:28,010
you should worship them as their son.

140
00:11:28,010 --> 00:11:29,800
I understand it.

141
00:11:29,800 --> 00:11:32,020
I will serve incense in the mansion

142
00:11:32,020 --> 00:11:35,290
to thank my parents for giving me my life.

143
00:11:35,290 --> 00:11:38,539
Mother, if it weren't for you to save me

144
00:11:38,539 --> 00:11:40,399
and to take good care of me for so many years,

145
00:11:40,400 --> 00:11:42,120
there wouldn't be me now.

146
00:11:42,120 --> 00:11:44,039
If my biological parents knew it,

147
00:11:44,040 --> 00:11:46,220
they would also be grateful to you.

148
00:11:47,430 --> 00:11:51,300
I still want to serve you just as before.

149
00:11:54,910 --> 00:11:56,510
I don't know...

150
00:11:57,990 --> 00:12:00,550
I don't know if you still want me to stay by your side.

151
00:12:03,840 --> 00:12:05,540
Get up.

152
00:12:09,400 --> 00:12:11,199
I never said I didn't want you.

153
00:12:11,200 --> 00:12:14,810
You and Jinli are both my children.

154
00:12:14,810 --> 00:12:16,610
You were my son before,

155
00:12:16,610 --> 00:12:18,420
you are my son now,

156
00:12:18,420 --> 00:12:20,780
and you will always be my son.

157
00:12:20,780 --> 00:12:24,279
- Do you remember it?
- Yes, I remember it.

158
00:12:25,690 --> 00:12:27,190
Mother.

159
00:12:46,400 --> 00:12:50,079
